<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق ذ ع:</span> <span class="c2">(قَذَعَهُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَقْذَعَهُ)</span> أَيْ رَمَاهُ بِالْفُحْشِ وَشَتَمَهُ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> «مَنْ قَالَ فِي الْإِسْلَامِ شِعْرًا <span class="c2">(مُقْذِعًا)</span> فَلِسَانُهُ هَدَرٌ» .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>